   deORBIT is a non-linear, non-combat first person puzzle  with  some
   rogue like elements and a slight  horror vibe.  You wake  up  in  a
   semi-destroyed space colony, power is out, oxygen  is  running  low
   and you must make your way out by smashing,  repairing, discovering
   alternate paths and improvising on the spot.  No  two  playthroughs
   will be the same! Four story lines are intertwined but it  is  only
   up to you to discover what brought you here, and only up to  you to
   get out alive.
 
  For more info go to : http://store.steampowered.com/app/337700/
